# verifiably-go runtime state
# - config/*.json is rendered from deploy.sh stanzas on every `deploy.sh run`
# - *.docker.json / *.rendered.yml are ephemeral docker-internal overrides
# - wso2is.env is written by scripts/bootstrap-wso2is.sh
# - locales/*.json is the LibreTranslate disk cache
# - walletbag.json persists the demo wallet credentials between runs
# - cookies.txt is a curl/test artifact
